                  <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="177309080052"></xptr>Q. Did you see any lead with me?</p>
               <p>Wheston. His coat was over it, and I stopped it on the other man.</p>
               <p>Scarborough's Defence.</p>
               <p>Kirk was not in the cellar, but he put his coat over it to cover it.</p>
               <p>Kirk's Defence.</p>
               <p>I carried no lead at all away.</p>
